{"tid":410440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普兒子原來踢中場 現效力華盛頓聯隊U12","createTime":"2017-09-23T02:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T04:15:48.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e30173cb7ee1e8ca55ae424be05aca0b310aedac","tid":410440,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=J856HIiPruNH7HKwC4Wa2MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=37237554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育<br />\n54 分鐘前<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=J856HIiPruNH7HKwC4Wa2MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=37237554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】足球在美國雖然愈來愈受重視，但仍然屈居於4大運動之後，不過美國總統特朗普的愛兒巴倫，原來是足球員，司職中場。<br />\n<br />\n巴倫（Barron Trump）是特朗普和第一夫人梅拉尼婭的獨生子，原來這名11歲小伙子是美職球隊華盛頓聯隊的U12成員，司職中場，身穿81號球衣。在周六，他將在本季第5度為球隊上陣，對戰PA Classic。 <br />\n<br />\n早前，巴倫就已經被傳媒拍得在<span style=\"color: red;\">白宮身穿阿仙奴的波褲及波襪，或者他是兵工廠的球迷。</span>若阿仙奴他日在美國進行友賽，未知巴倫和特朗普會否成為座上客？ 兒子是足球迷，原來特朗普也和足球有一段歷史。這名美國總統在1992年曾獲邀出席英聯盃的抽籤，更親手抽出列斯聯鬥曼聯這個宿敵對決，當時主持人看見對碰已大叫：「你沒有意識到你在這裡做了什麼！」，其後特朗普坦言：「這看來是一場我想去觀看的比賽。」"},{"pid":"c308dffbafe76a0c709d551154e3f81c8ca37da5","tid":410440,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T02:56:40.000Z","msg":"雲加又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5bd94868f4923afd374cd723e0ad3023fc7e3a","tid":410440,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef79b641d5c6389ecafe148c78fe2dade1a0ff59","tid":410440,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"雲加在下一個很大的棋"},{"pid":"8d8cbc1ebd4284123099763d755ebdde5361a6c9","tid":410440,"uid":9581,"